---
import ExperienceCard from "./experience/ExperienceCard.astro";
import ExperienceItem from "./experience/ExperienceItem.astro";

import giftbit from "../assets/giftbit.png";
import cuboh from "../assets/cuboh.png";
import freshworks from "../assets/freshworks.png";
import cpoqh from "../assets/cpohq.png";
import workday from "../assets/workday.png";
import ibm from "../assets/ibm.png";
---

<div class="welcome">
  <h1>Hi there! My name is Adam Dubicki.</h1>
  <div class="section" id="about-me">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <hr />
    <p>
      I'm a full-stack dev living in beautiful Victoria, BC. I've been building
      for the web since finishing my CS degree at UVic back in 2017. These days,
      I spend most of my building backends with Spring Boot, NestJS, and
      Node.js, but I'm always down to talk shop about new frameworks or clean
      code. When I'm not staring at a terminal, I'm usually trying to tire
      myself out. In the summer, that means long distance or hiking up Mt.
      Finlayson. When it's too cold for the trails, you'll find me staying warm
      inside with a great book or a board game.
    </p>
    <p>
      I am self-taught in scratchboard art. I mostly draw animals. My designs
      can be purchased on <a
        class="text-primary"
        rel="noreferrer"
        href="https://www.redbubble.com/people/adubicki/explore?asc=u&page=1&sortOrder=recent" target="_blank"
      >
        redbubble.</a
      > For other updates you can follow me on <a
        class="text-primary"
        href="https://www.instagram.com/a.j.dubicki" target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer">instagram.</a
      >
    </p>
    <iframe
      height="200"
      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-4wPE_KlKz4"
      title="YouTube video player"
      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
      allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
  </div>
  <div class="section" id="experience">
    <h2>Experience</h2>
    <hr />
    <ExperienceCard
      company="Workday"
      img={workday}
      skills={[
        "Kotlin",
        "Python",
        "Typescript",
        "Spring Boot",
        "React",
        "Jenkins",
        "Docker",
        "Kubernetes",
        "Helm",
        "Apache Superset",
        "Apache Airflow",
        "PySpark",
        "Elasticsearch",
        "Grafana",
      ]}
    >
      <ExperienceItem
        from="Jul 2023"
        to="Present"
        position="P3 Software Development Engineer"
      >
        <ul>
          <li>
            Orchestrated zero-downtime traffic migrations, implementing dynamic
            REST routing and phased rollout strategies for critical API
            endpoints.
          </li>
          <li>
            Architected a multi-year strategic decoupling of our monolithic
            repository, managing a massive roadmap to enhance system modularity
            and scalability.
          </li>
          <li>
            Spearheaded incident triage and resolution for high-availability
            production systems, maintaining strict SLAs and minimizing downtime
            through root-cause analysis.
          </li>

          <li>
            Engineered robust CI/CD pipelines and automated workflows,
            proactively resolving build failures and cross-functional blockers
            to sustain high developer velocity.
          </li>

          <li>
            Developed the first GenAI/LLM production feature at Workday,
            delivering article summarization and translation for Knowledge
            Management.
          </li>

          <li>
            Served as Agile Lead/Coach, optimizing team performance by
            facilitating sprint planning, refinement, and two-week delivery
            cycles for a high-output engineering team.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </ExperienceItem>
    </ExperienceCard>
    <ExperienceCard
      company="CPOHQ | Knoetic"
      img={cpoqh}
      skills={[
        "Typescript",
        "DBT",
        "React",
        "Snowflake",
        "Apache Airflow",
        "Cube-JS",
      ]}
    >
      <ExperienceItem
        from="Nov 2022"
        to="Mar 2023"
        position="Senior Full Stack Software Developer "
      >
        <ul>
          <li>
            Improved data quality by approximately 10% by identifying and
            addressing issues within the data-transform pipeline
          </li>
          <li>
            Led demos and presentations within a demo-driven environment to
            effectively communicate findings and solutions to company
            stakeholders
          </li>
        </ul>
      </ExperienceItem>
    </ExperienceCard>
    <ExperienceCard
      company="Cuboh (acquired by Chownow)"
      img={cuboh}
      skills={[
        "Typescript",
        "React",
        "React Native",
        "Cube-JS",
        "Python",
        "Django",
        "AWS",
        "Serverless",
        "Heroku",
      ]}
    >
      <ExperienceItem from="Nov 2021" to="Nov 2022" position="Technical Lead">
        <ul>
          <li>
            Successfully led a team in migrating microservices from Heroku to
            AWS resulting in $4,000/month cost savings
          </li>
          <li>
