            pre-aggregation techniques, resulting in a significant reduction in
            report generation time from over 10 seconds to under 2 seconds for
            reports containing 100,000 rows
          </li>
          <li>
            Mentored junior developer and team on best practices. Worked
            extensively with product and UX to help shape features to delight
            our customers
          </li>
          <li>
            Developed RESTful APIs and backend services in a service-oriented
            architecture
          </li>
        </ul>
      </ExperienceItem>
      <ExperienceItem
        from="May 2020"
        to="Nov 2021"
        position="Full Stack Software Developer"
      >
        <ul>
          <li>
            Achieved a significant reduction in incoming network requests of
            approximately 95% by optimizing the infrastructure between services.
          </li>
          <li>
            Automated onboarding process to reduce customer onboarding time from
            6 weeks to less than 1 week
          </li>
          <li>
            Doubled the performance of the mobile application by refactoring the
            application to be event driven
          </li>
        </ul>
      </ExperienceItem>
    </ExperienceCard>
    <ExperienceCard
      company="Freshworks Studio (acquired by EY)"
      img={freshworks}
      skills={[
        "PHP",
        "Laravel",
        "Typescript",
        "NextJS",
        "NestJS",
        "AWS",
        "Serverless Framework",
      ]}
    >
      <ExperienceItem
        from="Oct 2017"
        to="May 2020"
        position="Full Stack Developer"
      >
        <ul>
          <li>
            Optimized application performance for A Place for Mom by
            architecting a custom caching layer, successfully reducing
            first-render time to under 2 seconds.
          </li>
          <li>
            Engineered a reusable JSON-to-HealthVault translation library,
            streamlining data interactions and reducing boilerplate code by
            ~90%.
          </li>
          <li>
            Hardened the Foundry BC backend to achieve full compliance with
            PIPEDA, FOIPPA, PIPA, and BC OCIO security standards, ensuring data
            privacy.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </ExperienceItem>
    </ExperienceCard>
    <ExperienceCard
      company="Giftbit"
      img={giftbit}
      skills={["Grails", "Groovy", "Typescript", "AWS", "Flyway Migrate"]}
    >
