        from="May 2016"
        to="Dec 2016"
        position="Junior Backend Software Developer"
      >
        <ul>
          <li>
            Developed and optimized RESTful API with unit/integration testing.
          </li>

          <li>
            Managed back-end deployments and database migrations on AWS
            Beanstalk.
          </li>

          <li>Implemented 2FA by integrating a Twilio-based SMS solution.</li>

          <li>
