<div class="section" id="projects">
  <h2>Projects</h2>
  <hr />
    <ExperienceCard
      company="TypeORM Entity Factory"
      skills={["Typescript", "NestJS", "TypeORM"]}
    >
      <ExperienceItem from="Apr 2020" to="Jun 2022" position="NPM Package (Archived)" />
      <ul>
        <li>
          Inspired by Laravel data factories. A lightweight and flexible utility designed to simplify the creation of mock data for testing in applications using TypeORM.
        </li>

        <li>
         Instead of manually instantiating complex objects with dummy data every time you write a test, you define a blueprint once and let the factory handle the heavy lifting.
        </li>

        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/adamdubicki/typeorm-entity-factory" target="_blank">Repository</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </ExperienceCard>
</div>
<div class="section" id="contact">
  <h2>Contact</h2>
