  <a href="mailto:adamdubicki@outlook.com" target="_blank"
    ><b>Email</b> - adamdubicki(at)outlook.com</a
  >
  <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/adam-dubicki/" target="_blank"
    ><b>Linkedin</b> - https://www.linkedin.com/in/adam-dubicki/</a
  >
  <a href="https://github.com/adamdubicki" target="_blank"
    ><b>Github</b> - https://github.com/adamdubicki</a
  >
  <a
    href="https://www.redbubble.com/people/adubicki/explore?asc=u&page=1&sortOrder=recent" target="_blank"
    ><b>Redbubble</b> https://www.redbubble.com/people/adubicki</a
  >
</div>

